title: Athlete of the Week - Leonor Nickell
text:

Leonor Nickell - River Ridge - VolleyballLeonor Nickell helped the River Ridge volleyball team to a 5-6 record over the last two weeks, with the Lady Knights recording wins over North Cobb, Paideia, Creekview, Cass and Cherokee.Nickell had well-rounded matches, totaling 27 kills, 31 blocks and seven digs.
